// Dismiss UI Tool
// Clears the browser question panel by sending a dismiss request to the server.
// Called after a user answers a question in the terminal so the UI doesn't linger.

API base URL is configured via PORT (default 3737) and HOST (default localhost) environment variables.

FUNCTION buildUrl(path, project, session) -> string
  Construct an absolute URL with project and session as query parameters.

---

FUNCTION dismissUI(project, session) -> string                                   EXPORT
  POST to /api/dismiss-ui for the given project and session.
  Throw if the request fails. Return JSON string with { success: true, message }.
